        <item>
            <title>康文署 SmartPLAY 启用即「网络错误」  网民投诉：扣钱后无预约纪录</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/09/smartplay-fail/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=smartplay-fail</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/09/smartplay-fail/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 06:27:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iAM Smart]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SmartPLAY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[康文署]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智方便]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1203533</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港运动场地「炒场」问题严重，为遏止炒风，让真正用家可以享受康乐及文化事务署旗下的运动场地，康文署早前宣布推出「SmartPLAY 康体通」智能康体服务预订资讯系统，新系统于今晨（11 月 9 日） 7 时正式启动，但网上有不少用家表示无法登入境或预订场地。据明报报道，创新科技及工业局指，资科办现时正向康文署了解相关技术问题。</p><p>香港 LIHKG 讨论区网民「小薯茄 Kelsi 老公」今日上午 7 时尝试登入「SmartPLAY」预约羽毛球场，但系统一直弹出警告讯息，以及出现「网络错误」的讯息。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-299x580.jpg" alt="" width="299" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-299x580.jpg 299w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-464x900.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-768x1490.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-792x1536.jpg 792w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/t6Lj5Yw-scaled.jpg 825w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 299px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/bEakfwV">小薯茄 Kelsi 老公@LIHKG</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-299x580.jpg" alt="" width="299" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-299x580.jpg 299w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-464x900.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-768x1490.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-792x1536.jpg 792w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-1056x2048.jpg 825w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/hh9Uaqa-scaled.jpg 824w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 299px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/bEakfwV">小薯茄 Kelsi 老公@LIHKG</a></p><p>即使成功登入「SmartPLAY」应用程式亦不代表用家已成功预订场地。LIHKG 讨论区有用家「生见爱瑠」及「Brendalolo」均表示自己已支付预约费用，而且收到信用卡公司传送的付款成功短讯，可是在「SmartPLAY」应用程式上没有其预约纪录，拨打查询热线亦无人接听，亦没有收到预约确认的电邮。下面有热心网友「由嫩入稚」表示，要收到 SmartPLAY 的确认 PDF 才算预约成功。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140241-694x217.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="217" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140241-694x217.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140241-768x240.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140241.jpg 885w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/bEakhqV">生见爱瑠@LIHKG</a></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203690" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-141406-694x227.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="227" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-141406-694x227.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-141406-768x251.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-141406.jpg 887w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/BfmBxzX">Brendalolo@LIHKG</a></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140537-694x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140537-694x580.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/萤幕撷取画面-2023-11-09-140537.jpg 885w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/bEakhwV">由嫩入稚@LIHKG</a></p><p>明报引述一名议员表示，其今晨亦曾亲身尝试用「智方便」登入系统，但在认证过程期间不断被「弹出」，另外亦有市民向该议员反映无法登入「SmartPLAY」系统。议员表示无法理解为何康文署花长时间准备仍然落得如斯状况。LIHKG 讨论区上亦有会员反映指其于上午 9 时 45 分经「智方便」登入「SmartPLAY」，「SmartPLAY」页面却显示尚未启用的画面。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1203689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kTrzbiC-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kTrzbiC-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kTrzbiC-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kTrzbiC.png 739w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/kTrzbiC-709x1536.png 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://lih.kg/BfmBxsX">莫国关@LIHKG</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20231109/s00001/1699503799179/">明报</a>、<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BA%B7%E6%96%87%E7%BD%B2smartplay%E9%A6%96%E6%97%A5%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8-%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-033621500.html">on.cc</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3548271/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/09/smartplay-fail/hottopic/spotlight/">康文署 SmartPLAY 启用即「网络错误」  网民投诉：扣钱后无预约纪录</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
