        <item>
            <title>Google 联同欧洲电讯商，向欧盟倡议强制 Apple 开放 iMessage</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/09/google-and-carriers-ask-the-eu-to-make-imessage-a-core-platform/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-and-carriers-ask-the-eu-to-make-imessage-a-core-platform</link>
